---
title: Korma Spiced Butternut Squash Pie with Cheesy Mash Top and Green Beans
description: Pies are comforting and perfect for autumn, plus they don't need meat to be a real comfort food. Here, we're using warming korma curry paste to spice up the butternut squash filling for a delicious veggie meal.
